1
00:00:13,279 --> 00:00:14,496
(They say)

2
00:00:15,360 --> 00:00:17,140
(footprints don't last in the desert.)

3
00:00:18,379 --> 00:00:21,140
(One gust, and they're gone.)

4
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:26,800
(But I still remember
that mud-covered fool)

5
00:00:27,199 --> 00:00:28,460
(crouching on the dune)

6
00:00:29,199 --> 00:00:31,000
(and telling me he wanted to be a hero)

7
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:33,920
(with his eyes shining fiercely.)

8
00:00:35,939 --> 00:00:37,780
(I've watched Meng Guangcai
all the way.)

9
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:41,024
(Everyone is responsible for ensuring work safety)
(The boy who fought thugs)

10
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:43,780
(with his life back then)

11
00:00:46,299 --> 00:00:47,799
(kicked destiny's door)

12
00:00:49,079 --> 00:00:50,939
(Beiyan Shaliang Rural Credit Union)
(wide open in 1993.)

13
00:00:55,799 --> 00:00:56,700
(Since then,)

14
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,560
(he became different.)

15
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,920
(I watched helplessly)

16
00:01:01,380 --> 00:01:03,240
(as his path grew ever more brutal)

17
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:05,260
(and tainted.)

18
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:08,280
(He became a thorn)

19
00:01:09,959 --> 00:01:11,040
(sinking deeper and deeper)

20
00:01:13,180 --> 00:01:14,459
(in my heart.)

21
00:01:18,579 --> 00:01:21,620
(After 18 years of wind and sand,)

22
00:01:23,859 --> 00:01:25,359
(that thorn piercing my heart)

23
00:01:26,620 --> 00:01:28,159
(finally stirred.)

24
00:01:40,620 --> 00:01:41,400
Meng Xiaoliang,

25
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,760
the only son of Meng Guangcai,

26
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:43,936
chairman of Caisheng Group,

27
00:01:43,968 --> 00:01:45,260
(Li Quanyi, Captain of the Criminal Police Technical Unit, Beiyan)
Beiyan's prospective listed company.

28
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:48,260
During our DNA screening and comparison,

29
00:01:48,579 --> 00:01:49,620
(Liu Hua, Deputy Chief, Beiyan Police)
we unexpectedly discovered

30
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:52,719
that he and blood sample No. 3
found at the 6.10 crime scene

31
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:53,900
are son and father.

32
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:55,540
(Basic Info)

33
00:01:55,540 --> 00:01:59,180
We can basically determine
Meng Guangcai is a prime suspect.

34
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:02,819
(Zhang Wei, Captain of the Criminal Police, Beiyan)
Chief, we need an immediate task force

35
00:02:02,819 --> 00:02:03,859
to reopen the 6.10 case.

36
00:02:03,859 --> 00:02:04,700
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

37
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:05,799
(With leadership approval,)

38
00:02:06,540 --> 00:02:08,608
(Successful Signing Ceremony)
(we're reopening)

39
00:02:08,608 --> 00:02:11,620
(the 6.10 credit union
robbery‑murder case.)

40
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:15,200
(Meng Guangcai, Chairman of Caisheng Group)
Caisheng Group will be

41
00:02:15,392 --> 00:02:17,539
Beiyan's first listed company in Gang City.

42
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:23,680
(Given the latest public information,)

43
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:27,900
(Meng Guangcai, Caisheng Group chairman
and prime suspect in the 6.10 case,)

44
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:29,960
(will leave Beiyan City this afternoon)

45
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,879
(to attend business activities
in Europe.)

46
00:02:36,259 --> 00:02:37,099
You guys go ahead.

47
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,664
(Xue Qin, Meng Guangcai's wife)

48
00:02:59,234 --> 00:03:01,205
(1st Interrogation)

49
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:09,240
We are the Beiyan Police's
Criminal Investigation Unit.

50
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,800
You are being questioned by law.
Answer honestly.

51
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:12,800
Name?

52
00:03:13,659 --> 00:03:15,020
You've taken him into custody.

53
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:18,379
But when the time limit expires,
you'll have to release him.

54
00:03:18,599 --> 00:03:19,960
Find a breakthrough quickly.

55
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:24,879
Meng Guangcai, 49,
Chairman of Caisheng Group, Beiyan City.

56
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:27,460
Someone as important as you

57
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:31,400
should understand citizens have a duty
to cooperate with police investigations.

58
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:38,659
Meng Guangcai.

59
00:03:46,176 --> 00:03:47,264
(Xue Qin)

60
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,620
Hello?

61
00:03:54,432 --> 00:03:56,672
(Jiao Lijun,
General Manager of Caisheng Group)

62
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,759
Meng Guangcai!

63
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:06,939
Don't forget how you crawled
out of Shaguai Village.

64
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:10,319
Think carefully.

65
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,599
If we didn't have solid evidence,

66
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:15,360
why would we bring you in today?

67
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:38,600
Officer Zhu.

68
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:47,160
I know you're watching me.

69
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,160
Why not come out and meet me?

70
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,920
(The truth buried for 18 years)

71
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,040
(Zhu Helai, Logistics Support Officer,
Beiyan Police)

72
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,439
(deserves to see the light.)

73
00:06:15,296 --> 00:06:18,016
=The Silent Rift=

74
00:06:18,272 --> 00:06:21,000
=Episode 1=
(You're Not Getting Out)

75
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:24,500
Just now, at a reception by Caisheng,
our city's star enterprise,

76
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:27,100
Chairman Meng Guangcai
was suddenly taken away by police.

77
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:29,699
Relevant authorities
have yet to release official details.

78
00:06:29,980 --> 00:06:33,319
(Beiyan Evening News)
(But it has rocked the business world.)

79
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:35,879
(Caisheng Group
may face significant challenges.)

80
00:06:36,319 --> 00:06:39,720
(Beiyan Daily, Heishui Intersection)
(All eyes will be on how this unfolds.)

81
00:06:41,312 --> 00:06:42,199
(Successful Signing Ceremony)

82
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:44,379
You know how important Caisheng Group is

83
00:06:44,699 --> 00:06:45,759
to our city.

84
00:06:46,259 --> 00:06:47,939
My phone hasn't stopped ringing today.

85
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:50,319
Everyone is concerned about this case.

86
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:51,939
We're in a very awkward position.

87
00:06:52,259 --> 00:06:53,759
But this time is different, Chief.

88
00:06:54,259 --> 00:06:55,699
This time we have leads.

89
00:06:55,699 --> 00:06:57,660
I guarantee
we can turn this situation around.

90
00:06:59,699 --> 00:07:00,379
Chief.

91
00:07:10,540 --> 00:07:13,259
Since you've already taken action,

92
00:07:13,379 --> 00:07:16,319
use this limited time
to find a breakthrough quickly.

93
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,439
Rest assured, Chief.

94
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:19,720
I will find a breakthrough
within 24 hours.

95
00:07:21,379 --> 00:07:22,379
Officer Zhu,

96
00:07:22,379 --> 00:07:25,879
if you don't show up,
I won't say another word.

97
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:13,839
Mr. Meng, you sure act differently now,

98
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,939
calling me out by name specifically.

99
00:08:19,199 --> 00:08:21,040
No matter who's interrogating me,

100
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:22,939
it's always you

101
00:08:23,699 --> 00:08:24,819
behind it all.

102
00:08:25,500 --> 00:08:26,639
Given our history,

103
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,139
let's skip the games.

104
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,939
Since you came in here,

105
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:37,539
the newspapers and websites outside
haven't let up on me.

106
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:39,379
In just half a day,

107
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:42,379
they've made me as famous as you.

108
00:08:42,820 --> 00:08:43,940
They're saying

109
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,700
I framed you.

110
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:53,580
Nonsense. They're making it up.

111
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:56,039
How could you ever harm me?

112
00:09:02,899 --> 00:09:04,700
Well, did they write

113
00:09:08,019 --> 00:09:09,399
that I saved your life?

114
00:09:15,139 --> 00:09:16,139
Have you forgotten?

115
00:09:16,460 --> 00:09:20,379
Twenty-eight years ago
in Shaguai Village, Magou Town,

116
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:21,960
I was the one who gave you blood.

117
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:25,720
Yes.

118
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:27,399
That I can't forget.

119
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:30,460
(The crackdown
had just started that year.)

120
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:33,820
(1983, Shaguai Village, Magou Town)
(We cadets were sent to the front.)

121
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:37,320
(It was my first arrest mission
as a police officer.)

122
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,960
Laosan, Laosi, you guys over there.

123
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:41,080
Laoda, you take this side.
We'll flank him.

124
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:42,279
Be careful.

125
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:42,940
Be careful.

126
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,320
Wh-what was that sound?

127
00:10:16,899 --> 00:10:19,539
(Shaguai Village School, Magou Town)
You stay right here. Don't go anywhere.

128
00:10:19,539 --> 00:10:20,399
I'll go check.

129
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:25,200
Let's go look too.

130
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:31,159
Who shot you?

131
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:33,080
Laoda!

132
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:33,639
What happened?

133
00:10:33,639 --> 00:10:34,220
Laoda!

134
00:10:36,460 --> 00:10:36,960
Over there.

135
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,200
Laosan, Laosi, after them!

136
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,080
- Go!
- After them!

137
00:10:40,928 --> 00:10:43,460
(Outpatient of Magou Town Clinic)

138
00:10:43,460 --> 00:10:44,539
Doctor, hurry!

139
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:46,440
Zhu, the suspect is under control.

140
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,279
Please be safe.

141
00:10:47,279 --> 00:10:48,960
Slow down. Be careful.

142
00:10:49,659 --> 00:10:50,320
Zhu!

143
00:10:51,100 --> 00:10:51,779
Zhu Helai!

144
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:53,200
Family should wait outside.

145
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:53,840
Doctor!

146
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,279
Thank you.

147
00:10:58,304 --> 00:11:00,768
(Outpatient of Magou Town Clinic)

148
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,580
Doctor, how is he?

149
00:11:07,879 --> 00:11:10,200
The patient is losing blood fast.
He needs a transfusion.

150
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:11,100
Take mine.

151
00:11:11,100 --> 00:11:11,899
- Take mine.
- Mine.

152
00:11:11,899 --> 00:11:12,960
- Take mine. I...
- Any of us can.

153
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,759
Quiet. Who has Type A blood?

154
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:16,340
The patient has Type A. Who is Type A?

155
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:18,200
I'm AB. Who is Type A?

156
00:11:18,899 --> 00:11:20,080
Check mine first.

157
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:22,019
You come with me.

158
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:45,320
You gave me blood and saved my life
back then. That, I can't forget.

159
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:53,960
Is this how you treat the person
who saved your life?

160
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,320
Also thanks to you,

161
00:11:59,279 --> 00:12:00,840
I was a perfectly good detective,

162
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:03,580
but I've been helping
in the kitchen for years.

163
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:08,200
(Now my hand that used to hold a gun
holds a kitchen knife.)

164
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:12,539
Speaking of the kitchen,

165
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:15,039
it's almost mealtime.

166
00:12:15,159 --> 00:12:16,080
You haven't eaten, huh?

167
00:12:16,460 --> 00:12:17,519
I'll go get some food.

168
00:12:18,019 --> 00:12:19,840
We can chat slowly after we've eaten.

169
00:12:34,304 --> 00:12:37,024
(Interrogation Room)

170
00:13:04,032 --> 00:13:04,779
(Beiyan Police Model Meritorious Collective
Commendation Conference)

171
00:13:04,779 --> 00:13:06,139
(Beiyan Police Auditorium, 1983)
(In this operation,)

172
00:13:06,399 --> 00:13:08,039
(we three basked in Laoda's glory.)

173
00:13:08,460 --> 00:13:10,580
(We fully embodied
the spirit of our school motto.)

174
00:13:11,580 --> 00:13:12,279
(Salute!)

175
00:13:13,519 --> 00:13:14,440
(School motto!)

176
00:13:14,659 --> 00:13:15,639
- (Loyalty!)
- (Loyalty!)

177
00:13:15,639 --> 00:13:16,580
- (Unity!)
- (Unity!)

178
00:13:16,580 --> 00:13:17,580
- (Rigor!)
- (Rigor!)

179
00:13:17,580 --> 00:13:18,399
- (Dedication!)
- (Dedication!)

180
00:13:18,820 --> 00:13:21,460
(Liu Hua, Beiyan Police Academy Cadet)
(He should be called Liu Unity.)

181
00:13:22,399 --> 00:13:23,200
(Zhu Helai, Beiyan Police Academy Cadet)
(Zhu Loyalty.)

182
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,279
(Lin Shan, Beiyan Police Academy Cadet)
(Then I must be Lin Rigor.)

183
00:13:25,279 --> 00:13:25,899
(Rigor.)

184
00:13:25,899 --> 00:13:27,200
(Only Dedication left for me?)

185
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,200
(Du Ming, Beiyan Police Academy Cadet)
(You're left with Dedication.)

186
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,000
(Dedication.)

187
00:13:29,899 --> 00:13:31,519
(From now on,)

188
00:13:31,519 --> 00:13:33,639
(no matter
where we're assigned to work,)

189
00:13:34,279 --> 00:13:35,200
(we four together)

190
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:37,320
- (will accomplish great things!)
- (Will accomplish great things!)

191
00:13:46,507 --> 00:13:49,760
(Gubei City)

192
00:13:57,279 --> 00:13:57,960
Lijun.

193
00:13:58,460 --> 00:14:00,820
(Wang Dazhu, Caisheng Group's Deputy GM)
Pack up. Let's go back to Beiyan.

194
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,340
Stop drinking tea.

195
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,320
Go back for what?

196
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:04,960
To snatch him back?

197
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:07,200
Guangcai was taken away.

198
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:09,899
We can't just sit here drinking tea
and watching, can we?

199
00:14:11,340 --> 00:14:14,580
Among the police who took
Guangcai away was Zhu Helai.

200
00:14:15,139 --> 00:14:15,960
What?

201
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:31,500
That old man is like a lingering ghost.

202
00:14:31,500 --> 00:14:33,779
On what grounds
did he take Guangcai away?

203
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,840
Never mind why they took
Guangcai away for now.

204
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:38,779
We need to pull Zhu Helai
off the table first.

205
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:42,080
If he gets involved,
it could easily lead to big trouble.

206
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,340
I'll have him taken care of.

207
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:45,460
Are you really grabbing him
from the police?

208
00:14:46,399 --> 00:14:47,440
Stay in Gubei for now.

209
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:49,899
Why should I stay in Gubei?

210
00:14:49,899 --> 00:14:51,100
Do what you need to do.

211
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:53,399
I've leaked the news
to the internet and the media.

212
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,320
Let's wait and see.

213
00:15:01,659 --> 00:15:02,460
Master.

214
00:15:05,220 --> 00:15:07,200
Are you sure we can do it
in such a short time?

215
00:15:07,779 --> 00:15:09,899
Meng Guangcai
is determined to drag this out.

216
00:15:09,899 --> 00:15:12,940
Listen. Ask Chief Liu for an extension
on the investigation immediately.

217
00:15:13,700 --> 00:15:16,340
No matter what,
isn't he just a businessman?

218
00:15:16,340 --> 00:15:19,460
If you'd known him for 28 years,
you wouldn't see him that way.

219
00:15:19,460 --> 00:15:22,500
I didn't see Jiao Lijun or Wang Dazhu
at the scene today.

220
00:15:22,820 --> 00:15:24,940
We need to keep a very tight grip
on these two guys.

221
00:15:25,340 --> 00:15:27,899
Don't worry, Master.
Both of them are under surveillance.

222
00:15:27,899 --> 00:15:28,700
No movement.

223
00:15:31,460 --> 00:15:33,019
That's exactly what's suspicious.

224
00:15:34,399 --> 00:15:35,220
Alright, you go.

225
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:12,200
Zhu, you once said

226
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:15,200
we're no different from real brothers,

227
00:16:16,159 --> 00:16:17,279
and we're family.

228
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:20,320
Is this how you treat your own brother?

229
00:16:20,580 --> 00:16:22,899
If you aren't hungry, we can just chat.

230
00:16:24,779 --> 00:16:26,519
On June 10, 1993,

231
00:16:28,539 --> 00:16:29,440
where were you?

232
00:16:37,039 --> 00:16:38,139
I should try it first.

233
00:16:43,139 --> 00:16:44,399
It tastes good.

234
00:16:49,779 --> 00:16:50,519
Zhu,

235
00:16:51,759 --> 00:16:52,840
you've become sly.

236
00:16:56,659 --> 00:16:58,019
You brought me here,

237
00:16:58,539 --> 00:16:59,320
and then?

238
00:16:59,779 --> 00:17:01,139
You hid yourself.

239
00:17:01,460 --> 00:17:02,440
You went to get food

240
00:17:03,139 --> 00:17:04,279
to interrupt me.

241
00:17:05,319 --> 00:17:07,079
Now you're springing
this surprise on me.

242
00:17:08,779 --> 00:17:10,880
You weren't this scheming before.

243
00:17:28,864 --> 00:17:32,544
(Shaguai Village, Magou Town, 1983)

244
00:17:32,544 --> 00:17:34,272
(Shaguai Village)

245
00:17:49,180 --> 00:17:51,420
- I can pee higher!
- I can pee higher!

246
00:17:54,339 --> 00:17:55,680
I can pee higher!

247
00:18:06,519 --> 00:18:07,299
Class,

248
00:18:08,099 --> 00:18:10,180
open your textbooks to page 39.

249
00:18:10,799 --> 00:18:13,099
Today we'll learn 'The Peasants.'

250
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:16,539
Hungry, Mantang? Here.

251
00:18:16,539 --> 00:18:19,039
- Hoeing the grain under the noon sun.
- Hoeing the grain under the noon sun.

252
00:18:19,039 --> 00:18:19,680
Eat.

253
00:18:20,039 --> 00:18:20,940
- Sweat drips...
- Sweat drips...

254
00:18:20,940 --> 00:18:21,579
Take it.

255
00:18:21,579 --> 00:18:23,880
- down to the earth below.
- down to the earth below.

256
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:25,819
Brother Guangcai.

257
00:18:26,339 --> 00:18:27,099
Brother Guangcai.

258
00:18:27,099 --> 00:18:30,640
- Who knows that the food in the bowl
- Who knows that the food in the bowl

259
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:35,000
- is the fruit of bitter toil?
- is the fruit of bitter toil?

260
00:18:35,220 --> 00:18:36,440
Good. You recited that well.

261
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:38,539
Principal Chen,
Officer Zhu is here to see you.

262
00:18:40,599 --> 00:18:43,059
Copy this three times.

263
00:18:43,579 --> 00:18:44,720
(Chen Rongfa, Principal of Shaguai Village School)
I will step out for a moment.

264
00:18:48,259 --> 00:18:50,160
Principal Chen, Officer Zhu is here.

265
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,779
- Officer Zhu.
- Hello, Principal Chen.

266
00:18:51,779 --> 00:18:52,720
- This is Principal Chen.
- Hello.

267
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:54,500
He's also our village's
security director.

268
00:18:55,008 --> 00:18:55,776
Principal Chen,

269
00:18:55,776 --> 00:18:58,304
you, Brother Guangcai, and the others
helped me a lot earlier.

270
00:18:58,304 --> 00:19:00,660
Without you people,
I might not have made it.

271
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,440
Fully recovered?

272
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:03,539
Yes.

273
00:19:03,539 --> 00:19:04,920
Are you busy? Please go ahead.

274
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,420
Not at all. Come on.

275
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:07,019
Sit over here.

276
00:19:07,019 --> 00:19:08,039
- Sit over here.
- Sit.

277
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,180
They're doing homework.

278
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:11,559
Principal Chen, where's Meng Guangcai?

279
00:19:12,779 --> 00:19:13,680
Guangcai?

280
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:14,700
They're all out working.

281
00:19:14,700 --> 00:19:16,279
Maybe you should go ahead.

282
00:19:17,319 --> 00:19:18,039
He's back.

283
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,759
Zhu?

284
00:19:19,759 --> 00:19:20,680
Guangcai.

285
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:21,696
Brother Guangcai.

286
00:19:22,940 --> 00:19:23,680
Zhu.

287
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,599
Here are some powdered milk and cans.

288
00:19:27,599 --> 00:19:28,579
Build up your strength.

289
00:19:28,799 --> 00:19:29,400
No need.

290
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:29,960
Take them.

291
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,339
You don't have to.

292
00:19:31,339 --> 00:19:31,880
Take them.

293
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:33,339
Come on. Sit, Zhu.

294
00:19:33,339 --> 00:19:34,440
- Guangcai.
- Sit.

295
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:35,500
And these two men are?

296
00:19:36,599 --> 00:19:38,160
The three of us grew up together.

297
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,180
This is Jiao Lijun.

298
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:40,839
Zhu.

299
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:42,680
And this is...

300
00:19:42,680 --> 00:19:43,700
Wang Dazhu.

301
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:44,440
Yeah, Wang Dazhu.

302
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,180
Hello, hero.

303
00:19:45,180 --> 00:19:45,940
- Yes, Dazhu.
- Hello.

304
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:47,539
Her name is Qin.

305
00:19:47,940 --> 00:19:49,720
They were betrothed since childhood.

306
00:19:51,299 --> 00:19:52,019
Hello.

307
00:19:53,839 --> 00:19:54,700
Zhu, have a seat.

308
00:19:54,700 --> 00:19:56,579
- Sit.
- Sit.

309
00:19:56,799 --> 00:19:57,940
Qin, make some tea.

310
00:19:58,099 --> 00:19:59,420
- Got it.
- Just a moment.

311
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:00,680
No need to be so polite.

312
00:20:02,799 --> 00:20:03,960
How's your recovery going?

313
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:05,000
Quite well.

314
00:20:09,559 --> 00:20:11,400
Mantang, stop messing around.

315
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:13,440
- Stop messing around.
- Stop messing around.

316
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:14,380
Stop hitting him.

317
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:16,420
No hitting. No hitting. Don't bully him.

318
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:18,180
Go, all of you. Go home.

319
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:19,000
Go.

320
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:19,680
Go on.

321
00:20:20,599 --> 00:20:21,559
Who is this kid?

322
00:20:22,319 --> 00:20:23,259
He's Huang Mantang.

323
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:26,140
His father racked up
a lot of gambling debts in the village.

324
00:20:26,460 --> 00:20:28,440
Now this kid is also hopeless.

325
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:30,000
He relies on handouts every day.

326
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:32,079
Only Principal Chen
looks after him a bit more.

327
00:20:33,339 --> 00:20:35,000
Principal Chen, it must've been tough.

328
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,920
Zhu, chat with Principal Chen.

329
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:37,984
I'll see how Qin is doing.

330
00:20:37,984 --> 00:20:39,400
Brother Guangcai, no need for that.

331
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,779
We're poor. Nothing fancy to eat.

332
00:20:40,779 --> 00:20:41,660
Hope you won't mind.

333
00:20:41,660 --> 00:20:44,420
Don't stand on ceremony.
Let me get you something good.

334
00:20:44,420 --> 00:20:45,099
Just a moment.

335
00:20:45,700 --> 00:20:46,779
Almost ready.

336
00:20:46,779 --> 00:20:47,392
Huang Mantang.

337
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:51,039
Where's the thing
I told you to hide last time?

338
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:53,599
Bring it out.

339
00:20:53,779 --> 00:20:55,720
Don't burn yourself. Easy.

340
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,920
Here. Look, we made these ourselves.

341
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:00,680
You made these?

342
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:02,380
I'll cook some more dishes for you.

343
00:21:02,599 --> 00:21:03,180
Go play.

344
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:04,940
Guangcai. Guangcai.

345
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:06,059
Look.

346
00:21:08,180 --> 00:21:10,180
I stole it from my dad.

347
00:21:10,180 --> 00:21:12,180
Officer Zhu is here today.
Let's have a drink.

348
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:13,519
Open it.

349
00:21:13,519 --> 00:21:14,180
Let's drink.

350
00:21:14,559 --> 00:21:15,579
Xue Qin and Jiao.

351
00:21:16,064 --> 00:21:17,019
Sit too. Stop working.

352
00:21:17,019 --> 00:21:18,380
Alright, almost done.

353
00:21:18,839 --> 00:21:20,559
Last time you got injured on duty,

354
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:22,920
and Guangcai donated blood for you.

355
00:21:23,180 --> 00:21:25,200
He's mentioned it
at least a hundred times.

356
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:28,579
He said he helped a hero once,

357
00:21:28,779 --> 00:21:30,180
so he became a hero too.

358
00:21:30,180 --> 00:21:31,940
I never said I was a hero.

359
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:34,599
But Officer Zhu is here today
and can confirm.

360
00:21:34,599 --> 00:21:37,440
- Only I could donate blood that day.
- Yes.

361
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:39,420
I'm Type A, and you guys aren't, right?

362
00:21:39,779 --> 00:21:41,099
I saved a great hero.

363
00:21:41,099 --> 00:21:41,599
Zhu...

364
00:21:41,599 --> 00:21:43,940
Principal Chen,
I want to say something too.

365
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:47,680
Last time, Guangcai donated blood
to save my life.

366
00:21:48,019 --> 00:21:50,200
I truly don't know
how to express my gratitude.

367
00:21:50,799 --> 00:21:54,640
Brother Guangcai, from now on,
let's be like real brothers, okay?

368
00:21:58,039 --> 00:21:58,720
Officer Zhu,

369
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:02,420
please don't call me Brother Guangcai.
I'm surely younger than you.

370
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:04,220
Just call me Guangcai from now on.

371
00:22:04,880 --> 00:22:06,799
Then can I call you Zhu?

372
00:22:06,799 --> 00:22:08,660
Okay, just call me Zhu.

373
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:11,700
Moreover, I'm soon transferring
to the town's police station.

374
00:22:11,900 --> 00:22:14,380
In the future, as long
as it doesn't violate principles,

375
00:22:14,599 --> 00:22:15,539
you can make requests.

376
00:22:15,539 --> 00:22:16,539
Your word will work.

377
00:22:16,759 --> 00:22:18,079
Will what we say really work?

378
00:22:18,079 --> 00:22:19,079
Try saying something.

379
00:22:20,900 --> 00:22:21,500
Guangcai.

380
00:22:23,599 --> 00:22:25,000
Well, Zhu,

381
00:22:25,099 --> 00:22:27,539
do you know the movie
showing in town now?

382
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:30,420
Shaolin Temple.
Tickets are really hard to get.

383
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:34,400
I see. After we finish eating,

384
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:36,680
we all go together.

385
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:38,019
To town to see the movie.

386
00:22:38,299 --> 00:22:39,299
Really?

387
00:22:39,299 --> 00:22:40,440
- Thanks, Zhu!
- Thanks, Zhu!

388
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:42,039
- Thanks, Officer Zhu.
- Let's toast Officer Zhu.

389
00:22:42,039 --> 00:22:42,720
Come on.

390
00:22:42,940 --> 00:22:43,880
Here, Zhu, to you.

391
00:22:44,140 --> 00:22:45,019
Thanks.

392
00:22:53,519 --> 00:22:54,680
Look at you.

393
00:22:55,599 --> 00:22:57,640
If we could've been back in 1983,

394
00:22:58,500 --> 00:22:59,599
when we met,

395
00:23:00,319 --> 00:23:01,920
we could've shared another drink.

396
00:23:10,140 --> 00:23:12,420
You work in the kitchen now.

397
00:23:14,180 --> 00:23:15,940
You should've just cooked properly.

398
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:18,839
Caisheng Group didn't provoke you.

399
00:23:19,319 --> 00:23:21,920
Why did you have to drag me here today?

400
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:24,039
What good
does flipping the table do you?

401
00:23:25,019 --> 00:23:26,759
For Caisheng Group
to be where it is today,

402
00:23:27,720 --> 00:23:29,839
think about where
your first pot of gold came from.

403
00:23:30,180 --> 00:23:31,779
In June 1993,

404
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:35,880
you robbed the credit union
and fled south with Wang Dazhu.

405
00:23:36,759 --> 00:23:38,920
In 1995, you returned to Beiyan.

406
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:42,279
You pulled Jiao Lijun in to set up shop
and get into building materials.

407
00:23:42,279 --> 00:23:43,779
You took the money you robbed

408
00:23:44,140 --> 00:23:46,440
to run a building materials
and construction business.

409
00:23:47,019 --> 00:23:48,680
Then you founded the Caisheng Group.

410
00:23:49,039 --> 00:23:51,180
You've been quite the busy bee
all these years.

411
00:23:51,460 --> 00:23:52,279
Guangcai,

412
00:23:53,059 --> 00:23:54,079
to be honest,

413
00:23:55,279 --> 00:23:56,319
it's too conspicuous.

414
00:24:01,099 --> 00:24:04,680
Then you've been quite busy
all these years, haven't you?

415
00:24:05,259 --> 00:24:07,160
All these years,
I've only done one thing.

416
00:24:08,319 --> 00:24:09,680
That's investigating you.

417
00:24:11,519 --> 00:24:14,140
Investigating me must have been tough.

418
00:24:14,900 --> 00:24:16,200
You can say nothing.

419
00:24:17,180 --> 00:24:18,559
You can resist to the end.

420
00:24:18,940 --> 00:24:20,799
The fact that we brought you in today

421
00:24:22,019 --> 00:24:24,059
means we definitely have evidence.

422
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:27,680
Rest assured.

423
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,220
You're not getting out.

424
00:24:34,816 --> 00:24:35,519
(Caisheng Building)

425
00:24:35,519 --> 00:24:37,539
Guangcai is definitely innocent.

426
00:24:37,539 --> 00:24:39,920
This is absolutely true.
You must believe me.

427
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:43,500
Today is the group's press conference.

428
00:24:43,779 --> 00:24:46,259
Someone deliberately chose this day
to smear the group.

429
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:48,500
That's malicious intent.

430
00:24:49,099 --> 00:24:51,180
We must get Guangcai out quickly.

431
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:53,880
As the legal team
for the Caisheng Group,

432
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:56,099
we will actively cooperate
with the police.

433
00:24:56,779 --> 00:25:01,180
Caisheng Group operates
more than 20 companies in total

434
00:25:01,319 --> 00:25:03,559
in real estate, culture,
and finance in Beiyan.

435
00:25:03,559 --> 00:25:07,880
It's also Beiyan's first pre‑IPO company
with widespread attention.

436
00:25:08,259 --> 00:25:11,200
The implications here
are too significant.

437
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:12,880
Regarding your meeting request,

438
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:16,259
we will make a decision ASAP
within the stipulated time

439
00:25:16,900 --> 00:25:18,259
and notify you immediately.

440
00:25:18,259 --> 00:25:23,680
Can you disclose what Mr. Meng Guangcai
is actually involved in?

441
00:25:24,299 --> 00:25:25,180
We can't.

442
00:25:25,952 --> 00:25:27,339
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

443
00:25:27,339 --> 00:25:30,380
At approximately 13:17 on June 10, 1993,

444
00:25:30,779 --> 00:25:33,200
at the intersection of Wenhua Road
and Jianshe Road,

445
00:25:33,799 --> 00:25:36,919
the Native Produce Market Branch

446
00:25:36,919 --> 00:25:39,000
of Beiyan Credit Union was robbed.

447
00:25:40,299 --> 00:25:42,940
Over 590,000 yuan in cash
was robbed from the scene.

448
00:25:43,579 --> 00:25:45,539
According to statements
from five eyewitnesses,

449
00:25:45,839 --> 00:25:48,940
an armed robber and his two accomplices

450
00:25:48,940 --> 00:25:50,839
suddenly stormed in
and robbed the place.

451
00:25:51,299 --> 00:25:52,180
And unfortunately,

452
00:25:52,180 --> 00:25:55,180
during the process, one of our officers
was seriously injured.

453
00:25:56,319 --> 00:25:57,299
Alright.

454
00:25:58,000 --> 00:26:00,400
Three bloodstains
were left at the scene.

455
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:04,839
Two belonged to the credit union
security guard and Officer Lin Shan.

456
00:26:04,940 --> 00:26:05,880
As for the third one,

457
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:08,960
we suspected it was left by a robber.

458
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:11,279
But given the limited
forensic technology back then,

459
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:15,039
we couldn't confirm that the blood
belonged to Meng Guangcai.

460
00:26:15,420 --> 00:26:16,160
But now...

461
00:26:17,700 --> 00:26:19,680
I feel Meng Guangcai would never dream

462
00:26:20,180 --> 00:26:24,180
that Meng Xiaoliang's blood sample
and blood No. 3 show a paternity match.

463
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,839
Folks, it's been 18 years.

464
00:26:27,839 --> 00:26:29,039
I feel this didn't come easy.

465
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:32,920
We must seize this momentum
to get the full list of robbers.

466
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,680
Then let's just show him the evidence.

467
00:26:34,940 --> 00:26:35,960
He'll talk.

468
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:38,019
The blood type comparison results
aren't back yet.

469
00:26:38,180 --> 00:26:40,039
Isn't showing evidence now
a bit premature?

470
00:26:41,599 --> 00:26:44,380
Shouldn't we take advantage
of Meng Guangcai's uncertainty

471
00:26:45,059 --> 00:26:46,819
while he's still overthinking things

472
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:49,440
to get him to give away his accomplices?

473
00:26:50,299 --> 00:26:54,039
That's what you mean, Captain Li, right?

474
00:26:55,660 --> 00:26:56,539
I've said my piece.

475
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:06,720
Master, maybe you should head back
to the interrogation room?

476
00:27:09,420 --> 00:27:10,180
Zhu,

477
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,180
(2nd Interrogation)
back then, because of you,

478
00:27:14,380 --> 00:27:15,640
I offended Zuo Long.

479
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:17,920
But without you,

480
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:20,599
I couldn't have worked in Magou Town,

481
00:27:21,059 --> 00:27:23,099
and there would be
no Caisheng Group today.

482
00:27:26,019 --> 00:27:27,420
Thinking about it that way,

483
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,259
I really am grateful to you.

484
00:27:31,259 --> 00:27:34,180
If you'd known you'd become
Chairman of the Caisheng Group,

485
00:27:34,940 --> 00:27:36,880
you would have ignored
a small cop like me.

486
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:40,160
I used to be your protector.

487
00:27:41,099 --> 00:27:43,539
But after 1993, I became your problem.

488
00:27:46,599 --> 00:27:47,420
Guangcai,

489
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,400
actually, you changed long ago.

490
00:27:51,559 --> 00:27:53,180
You became someone like Zuo Long.

491
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:58,599
I'm not like him.

492
00:27:59,787 --> 00:28:02,432
(Magou Town, Beiyan County, 1988)

493
00:28:07,420 --> 00:28:08,160
Guangcai.

494
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:09,559
Zuo Long.

495
00:28:10,539 --> 00:28:11,180
Zuo Long.

496
00:28:12,256 --> 00:28:14,720
(Zuo Long)

497
00:28:14,720 --> 00:28:15,920
Huang Mantang owes you money?

498
00:28:16,799 --> 00:28:18,099
That's between you two.

499
00:28:18,539 --> 00:28:20,660
What gives you the right
to ask Principal Chen for it?

500
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:23,539
Hand over that hundred yuan today,
and this is over.

501
00:28:29,440 --> 00:28:31,039
Come on, move aside.

502
00:28:31,700 --> 00:28:34,940
Meng Guangcai,
I heard you saved some cop.

503
00:28:35,339 --> 00:28:37,700
What? Think you're some kind of hero?

504
00:28:41,460 --> 00:28:43,960
Huang Mantang skipped work
and wrecked my tractor.

505
00:28:44,319 --> 00:28:45,539
Let alone you.

506
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:48,460
Even if the police show up,
he's paying. Understand?

507
00:28:49,460 --> 00:28:51,680
Long, let's talk this out properly.

508
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:54,319
We're all from Shaguai.
We can reason this out.

509
00:28:54,460 --> 00:28:56,200
You pay back the money, and we'll leave.

510
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,279
We've worked at the mine for...

511
00:28:58,279 --> 00:28:59,680
Alright, stop nagging me.

512
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:00,579
Ask him.

513
00:29:01,940 --> 00:29:06,160
Every time I go to town for business,
that cop gives me trouble.

514
00:29:06,579 --> 00:29:09,920
He once dragged me to the station
and questioned me until midnight.

515
00:29:10,319 --> 00:29:11,700
I just couldn't figure it out.

516
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:16,519
Turns out, it was you guys who snitched.

517
00:29:16,519 --> 00:29:18,160
Especially you, Meng Guangcai.

518
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,400
What do you mean, 'snitched'?

519
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:20,640
You know what I mean.

520
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:22,440
How much trash
did you say behind my back?

521
00:29:22,900 --> 00:29:23,940
Let me tell you something.

522
00:29:23,940 --> 00:29:26,039
Nobody's leaving here
standing today. Got it?

523
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:29,759
The cops give you trouble,
so you take it out on us?

524
00:29:29,759 --> 00:29:31,660
- Last thing I need is your voice.
- What?

525
00:29:31,660 --> 00:29:32,380
Get him!

526
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,019
Stop!

527
00:29:38,220 --> 00:29:39,019
Qin, hold the bike.

528
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:40,299
What's going on?

529
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:45,180
Well, isn't this Officer Zhu?

530
00:29:45,440 --> 00:29:47,819
Zuo Long, you bully
and monopolize at the quarry.

531
00:29:48,180 --> 00:29:49,000
I can deal with you.

532
00:29:49,420 --> 00:29:51,420
Here, I can still deal with you.

533
00:29:52,180 --> 00:29:54,059
Have them put their things down.

534
00:29:57,380 --> 00:29:58,140
Officer Zhu,

535
00:29:58,900 --> 00:30:00,559
a debt must be paid, right?

536
00:30:00,759 --> 00:30:02,680
What? Helping him but not me?

537
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:05,799
I'll say it once more.
Everyone, put your things down.

538
00:30:05,940 --> 00:30:07,019
Or you'll all come with me.

539
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:08,559
Is that what you want?

540
00:30:12,299 --> 00:30:13,599
Alright then, Meng Guangcai.

541
00:30:14,799 --> 00:30:15,599
Just you wait.

542
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,299
Let's go.

543
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:22,720
Are you okay?

544
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:24,259
I'm fine.

545
00:30:28,819 --> 00:30:31,599
This afternoon, we went to Zuo Long.

546
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:35,079
He said the one hundred yuan from you
is down to just fifteen.

547
00:30:35,079 --> 00:30:36,319
We got it back for you.

548
00:30:46,180 --> 00:30:47,539
Take the money.

549
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:48,220
Take it.

550
00:30:49,779 --> 00:30:51,940
He actually gave the money back?

551
00:30:53,519 --> 00:30:55,079
He wasn't planning on giving it back.

552
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:58,140
Qin went to get Officer Zhu later.

553
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:01,400
When Zuo Long saw Officer Zhu, he froze.

554
00:31:02,079 --> 00:31:03,900
That's why
he gave back the fifteen yuan.

555
00:31:04,420 --> 00:31:05,519
Just take it.

556
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:09,079
He said he'll pay you back the rest.

557
00:31:09,599 --> 00:31:11,039
Well, thank Officer Zhu for me.

558
00:31:11,039 --> 00:31:11,779
Come eat.

559
00:31:12,736 --> 00:31:13,339
More for you.

560
00:31:13,339 --> 00:31:14,000
No. I'm good.

561
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:14,940
I can't eat.

562
00:31:15,460 --> 00:31:18,539
Here, there's more. It's Qin's favorite.

563
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:21,059
Thanks, Mr. Chen.

564
00:31:21,599 --> 00:31:22,279
Qin,

565
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:27,779
a few days ago, I saw something nice
at the supply and marketing cooperative.

566
00:31:27,779 --> 00:31:29,500
I bought it for Qin.

567
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:32,900
It's so pretty.

568
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:34,920
Mr. Chen understands Qin best.

569
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:36,160
Qin loves red.

570
00:31:36,940 --> 00:31:37,519
Let me help.

571
00:31:37,519 --> 00:31:39,200
Put it on.

572
00:31:42,528 --> 00:31:43,339
Does it look nice?

573
00:31:44,019 --> 00:31:44,519
Nice.

574
00:31:44,559 --> 00:31:45,299
Nice.

575
00:31:46,259 --> 00:31:46,839
Nice.

576
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:47,940
Nice.

577
00:31:47,940 --> 00:31:49,380
You all eat slowly.

578
00:31:49,839 --> 00:31:50,559
Really nice.

579
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:51,559
Eat up.

580
00:31:54,420 --> 00:31:56,680
Mr. Chen's eyesight
is getting worse and worse.

581
00:31:58,460 --> 00:31:59,880
Mr. Chen took the money.

582
00:32:00,259 --> 00:32:02,180
We still need to get the rest of it.

583
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:03,420
He doesn't believe it.

584
00:32:04,059 --> 00:32:05,440
Whether he believes it or not,

585
00:32:05,680 --> 00:32:08,019
we absolutely have to find a way
to make up that money.

586
00:32:24,819 --> 00:32:25,380
Guangcai!

587
00:32:25,559 --> 00:32:26,400
Guangcai!

588
00:32:36,519 --> 00:32:37,259
Feeling cocky?

589
00:32:39,279 --> 00:32:40,680
Where's that bravado from the day?

590
00:32:42,079 --> 00:32:42,920
Not so tough now?

591
00:32:44,500 --> 00:32:46,839
Didn't I say? It's not over.

592
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:50,019
This isn't over. What?

593
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:52,680
You thought
that Officer Zhu scared me off?

594
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:55,259
Let's see who can save you today.

595
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:57,819
You've hit them and vented your anger.

596
00:32:57,819 --> 00:32:59,180
What more do you want?

597
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,720
What do I want?

598
00:33:04,339 --> 00:33:05,680
You want me to let them go?

599
00:33:06,200 --> 00:33:07,140
No problem.

600
00:33:07,140 --> 00:33:08,700
Look at how poor you all are.

601
00:33:09,099 --> 00:33:10,460
If I want more, you can't pay.

602
00:33:10,460 --> 00:33:13,440
Here's the deal. 500 yuan.
Give me 500 yuan.

603
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:14,299
I'll let them go.

604
00:33:14,299 --> 00:33:15,220
I'll give you that.

605
00:33:15,779 --> 00:33:16,539
Now

606
00:33:16,539 --> 00:33:18,500
let me go.
I'll go home and get you the money.

607
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:23,420
How can you spew such nonsense?

608
00:33:24,779 --> 00:33:26,380
If I let you go and you run, what then?

609
00:33:26,380 --> 00:33:29,960
I won't run. Let me go. I'll go home
and get you the money, okay?

610
00:33:30,839 --> 00:33:31,339
Well.

611
00:33:32,180 --> 00:33:34,339
Look, I've thought of a way to help you.

612
00:33:35,599 --> 00:33:36,779
No problem if you don't pay.

613
00:33:39,079 --> 00:33:40,160
Just pay with yourself.

614
00:33:41,059 --> 00:33:42,299
You filthy scoundrel!

615
00:33:42,460 --> 00:33:44,059
Stay with me for three days.

616
00:33:44,059 --> 00:33:45,220
I'll let them all go, okay?

617
00:33:45,220 --> 00:33:46,420
Anything but this.

618
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:49,339
I'll agree to anything else you say.

619
00:33:49,460 --> 00:33:51,599
No money paid, and no company?

620
00:33:51,599 --> 00:33:54,019
Trying to trick me?
She's trying to trick me!

621
00:33:55,180 --> 00:33:58,799
Well. Look at yourself. Come on.

622
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:01,519
Take a good look. Come on. Brothers!

623
00:34:01,519 --> 00:34:02,279
Come take a look.

624
00:34:02,819 --> 00:34:04,519
Tell me, is she worth 500 yuan?

625
00:34:04,519 --> 00:34:05,779
- Not worth it!
- Not worth it!

626
00:34:05,779 --> 00:34:06,599
Hear that?

627
00:34:07,220 --> 00:34:09,659
Lowlifes, all lowlifes!

628
00:34:09,659 --> 00:34:13,059
Lowlifes hooking up with lowlifes,
breeding more lowlifes!

629
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:15,260
Dare to talk back to me?

630
00:34:22,300 --> 00:34:24,659
Look, don't say
I didn't try to help you.

631
00:34:26,500 --> 00:34:27,000
Come here.

632
00:34:28,659 --> 00:34:30,440
You, show them

633
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,860
how a lowlife crawls.

634
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:34,539
Crawl over here.
Crawl over, and I'll let them all go.

635
00:34:38,179 --> 00:34:38,900
Alright?

636
00:34:45,119 --> 00:34:45,900
What now?

637
00:34:46,900 --> 00:34:49,780
Not crawling? Don't want to crawl? Fine.

638
00:34:53,300 --> 00:34:54,880
I heard you two are betrothed.

639
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:58,760
Meng Guangcai,
childhood betrothal, right?

640
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:00,019
You won't crawl?

641
00:35:00,019 --> 00:35:01,500
Stop!

642
00:35:01,632 --> 00:35:02,519
Childhood betrothal?

643
00:35:02,519 --> 00:35:04,860
Stop it! You beast!

644
00:35:05,019 --> 00:35:05,960
- Stop!
- Crawl or not?

645
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:06,940
Stop it!

646
00:35:07,659 --> 00:35:09,119
Your woman's cold.

647
00:35:11,860 --> 00:35:14,539
Crawl or not? Crawl or not?

648
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:16,064
Not crawling? Still no?

649
00:35:16,064 --> 00:35:17,079
Stop!

650
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:18,079
Crawl or not?

651
00:35:20,179 --> 00:35:21,699
Come on. Bring the tractor over.

652
00:35:21,699 --> 00:35:24,599
Come on, drag him over. Hurry up.

653
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,780
Come on. Drive the tractor over.
Come on.

654
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,619
Come on. Hurry.

655
00:35:33,619 --> 00:35:35,280
Step on the gas. Give it gas.

656
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:38,079
Give it. Come on.

657
00:35:38,079 --> 00:35:40,719
Gas! Give it gas!

658
00:35:41,619 --> 00:35:44,340
Gas! Come on!

659
00:35:44,719 --> 00:35:46,360
Give it gas!

660
00:36:15,039 --> 00:36:16,119
I'll crawl.

661
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:18,019
Stop. Back up.

662
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,199
Make him behave.

663
00:36:26,420 --> 00:36:27,420
Come on, brothers.

664
00:36:27,420 --> 00:36:28,320
Come on, line up.

665
00:36:28,599 --> 00:36:30,280
Come on, hurry.

666
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:32,119
Come on, lowlife.

667
00:36:32,119 --> 00:36:33,199
Hurry up.

668
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:35,079
What took you? All lowlifes.

669
00:36:35,079 --> 00:36:35,599
Come on.

670
00:36:35,599 --> 00:36:36,539
- Hurry!
- Hurry!

671
00:36:38,659 --> 00:36:40,079
Hurry up! Quick!

672
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:41,679
- Hurry!
- Hurry!

673
00:36:43,860 --> 00:36:44,420
Come on.

674
00:36:44,619 --> 00:36:45,360
Come on. Hurry.

675
00:38:01,920 --> 00:38:05,380
(Outpatient of Magou Town Clinic)

676
00:38:05,380 --> 00:38:05,900
Doctor.

677
00:38:06,059 --> 00:38:07,099
Hello, officer.

678
00:38:07,860 --> 00:38:09,260
Which room is Meng Guangcai in?

679
00:38:09,599 --> 00:38:10,380
Exam Room Two.

680
00:38:10,380 --> 00:38:11,179
Okay, thanks.

681
00:38:13,219 --> 00:38:14,639
Does your head hurt, Guangcai?

682
00:38:15,539 --> 00:38:17,139
I didn't want Qin to see and worry.

683
00:38:18,139 --> 00:38:20,079
I asked Dazhu to take her home first.

684
00:38:21,539 --> 00:38:22,860
The doctor told me everything.

685
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:28,500
He said your shoulder
and ribs are fractured.

686
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:30,880
The worst is the blood in your urine.

687
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:32,639
The results aren't back yet.

688
00:38:34,199 --> 00:38:35,880
I've been thinking about this all night.

689
00:38:37,659 --> 00:38:41,119
Logically, we've been working
at the mine for a while now.

690
00:38:42,619 --> 00:38:45,179
Why would Zuo Long
suddenly turn against us?

691
00:38:45,639 --> 00:38:48,179
Just over Huang Mantang?
That shouldn't be it.

692
00:38:49,860 --> 00:38:50,860
When it comes down to it,

693
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:53,559
it's still because of Zhu.

694
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:58,039
Zhu is a good man, a hero.

695
00:38:58,659 --> 00:39:00,000
But he's a cop.

696
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:01,119
And Zuo Long?

697
00:39:01,820 --> 00:39:02,860
He's a thug, a hoodlum.

698
00:39:02,860 --> 00:39:04,039
They're like fire and water.

699
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,780
You're getting close to him now.

700
00:39:07,019 --> 00:39:09,039
That definitely doesn't sit well
with Zuo Long.

701
00:39:09,500 --> 00:39:11,380
We're working under him.

702
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:13,820
There'll be plenty of conflicts
in the future.

703
00:39:15,820 --> 00:39:18,860
Besides, the mine
is run by his brother-in-law.

704
00:39:20,039 --> 00:39:22,139
We definitely can't go back
to that mine after this.

705
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:25,880
I figure we'll have to head to town.

706
00:39:28,519 --> 00:39:31,500
But if we leave,
I'll worry about Mr. Chen and Qin.

707
00:39:33,039 --> 00:39:35,199
And it's different in the village
compared to town.

708
00:39:36,139 --> 00:39:37,800
We know people in the village.

709
00:39:38,260 --> 00:39:40,360
In town,
we won't know anyone or anything.

710
00:39:41,559 --> 00:39:42,639
There's only Zhu.

711
00:39:43,659 --> 00:39:46,360
But we can't bother Zhu with everything.

712
00:39:46,860 --> 00:39:48,260
Why can't you bother me?

713
00:39:49,059 --> 00:39:49,800
Zhu.

714
00:39:50,059 --> 00:39:50,760
Lijun.

715
00:39:57,579 --> 00:39:58,659
He's not well.

716
00:40:00,420 --> 00:40:01,260
Guangcai,

717
00:40:02,519 --> 00:40:03,420
take this money

718
00:40:06,880 --> 00:40:07,820
to Principal Chen.

719
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:15,219
It's not you he's scared of.

720
00:40:16,639 --> 00:40:19,519
He's scared of the uniform you wear.

721
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:26,579
Zhu, he means Zuo Long
isn't scared of the law behind you.

722
00:40:26,579 --> 00:40:27,619
He's scared of you.

723
00:40:28,719 --> 00:40:29,599
Stop talking.

724
00:40:31,159 --> 00:40:34,340
Zuo Long gathered a crowd to fight
and injured people.

725
00:40:34,519 --> 00:40:35,420
He won't get away.

726
00:40:35,860 --> 00:40:37,440
As for finding work,

727
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:40,260
come find me in Magou Town
once you heal.

728
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:48,000
Isn't it strange about Zuo Long?

729
00:40:49,400 --> 00:40:50,960
He vanished over 20 years ago.

730
00:40:51,639 --> 00:40:54,179
No sign of him alive.

731
00:40:55,059 --> 00:40:57,639
And no sign of him dead.

732
00:40:59,059 --> 00:41:00,500
Where do you think he went?

733
00:41:03,900 --> 00:41:04,840
Well,

734
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,820
you'd have to ask him that yourself.

735
00:41:27,520 --> 00:41:32,544
=The Silent Rift=
